    {
      "section_id": "para_33",
      "heading": "2.  Dalam Akta ini, melainkan jika konteksnya menghendaki makna \nyang lain—",
      "content": "2.  Dalam Akta ini, melainkan jika konteksnya menghendaki makna \nyang lain—",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_34",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "“melancung”  mempunyai  pengertian  yang  diberikan  kepadanya",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_35",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "oleh Kanun Keseksaan [Akta 574];",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_36",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "“syiling  semasa”  ertinya  apa-apa  syiling  yang  dijadikan  oleh",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_37",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "undang-undang, wang sah di Malaysia.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
